datasets.name: all_model_usage
queryLines:
SELECT
    u.request_time,
    DATE(u.request_time) as request_date,
    u.input_token_count,
    u.output_token_count,
    u.input_token_count + u.output_token_count as total_tokens,
    u.status_code,
    CASE WHEN u.status_code = 200 THEN 'Success' ELSE 'Error' END as status,
    u.requester,
    e.endpoint_name,
    COALESCE(e.served_entity_name, e.entity_name) as model_name,
    e.entity_name as model_version,
    CASE
        WHEN LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%claude%' OR LOWER(e.endpoint_name) LIKE '%claude%' THEN 'Anthropic'
        WHEN LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%gpt%' OR LOWER(e.endpoint_name) LIKE '%gpt%' OR LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%openai%' THEN 'OpenAI'
        WHEN LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%gemini%' OR LOWER(e.endpoint_name) LIKE '%gemini%' THEN 'Google'
        WHEN LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%llama%' OR LOWER(e.entity_name) LIKE '%meta%' THEN 'Meta'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END as provider
FROM system.serving.endpoint_usage u
JOIN system.serving.served_entities e
    ON u.served_entity_id = e.served_entity_id
WHERE e.entity_type = 'FOUNDATION_MODEL'
   OR e.external_model_config IS NOT NULL

datasets.name: all_model_billing
queryLines:
SELECT
    usage_date as request_date,
    usage_metadata.endpoint_name as endpoint_name,
    CASE
        WHEN sku_name LIKE '%ANTHROPIC%' THEN 'Anthropic'
        WHEN sku_name LIKE '%OPENAI%' THEN 'OpenAI'
        WHEN sku_name LIKE '%GOOGLE%' THEN 'Google'
        WHEN sku_name LIKE '%META%' OR sku_name LIKE '%LLAMA%' THEN 'Meta'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END as provider,
    sku_name,
    SUM(usage_quantity) as total_dbus,
    SUM(usage_quantity * COALESCE(lp.pricing.effective_list.default, 0.07)) as estimated_cost
FROM system.billing.usage u
LEFT JOIN system.billing.list_prices lp
    ON u.sku_name = lp.sku_name
    AND u.cloud = lp.cloud
    AND u.usage_start_time >= lp.price_start_time
    AND (lp.price_end_time IS NULL OR u.usage_start_time < lp.price_end_time)
WHERE u.sku_name LIKE '%MODEL_SERVING%'
   OR u.sku_name LIKE '%FOUNDATION_MODEL%'
GROUP BY usage_date, usage_metadata.endpoint_name, sku_name

datasets.name: ai_gateway_usage
queryLines:
SELECT
    request_time,
    DATE(request_time) as request_date,
    endpoint_name,
    model_name,
    CASE
        WHEN LOWER(model_name) LIKE '%claude%' THEN 'Anthropic'
        WHEN LOWER(model_name) LIKE '%gpt%' THEN 'OpenAI'
        WHEN LOWER(model_name) LIKE '%gemini%' THEN 'Google'
        WHEN LOWER(model_name) LIKE '%llama%' THEN 'Meta'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END as provider,
    input_token_count,
    output_token_count,
    total_token_count,
    request_latency_ms,
    time_to_first_token_ms,
    status_code,
    CASE WHEN status_code = 200 THEN 'Success' ELSE 'Error' END as status,
    requester,
    routing_information
FROM system.ai_gateway.usage

datasets.name: routing_data
queryLines:
SELECT
    request_time,
    DATE(request_time) as request_date,
    endpoint_name,
    model_name,
    routing_information,
    routing_information.served_model_name as routed_to,
    input_token_count,
    output_token_count,
    request_latency_ms,
    status_code,
    requester
FROM system.ai_gateway.usage
WHERE routing_information IS NOT NULL
